#: ../bugfixes/type1/guardapproachtarget.rst:7
msgid "Units in Guard Mission Will not Chase Aircraft"
msgstr ""

#: ../bugfixes/type1/guardapproachtarget.rst:9
msgid ""
"Units in Guard mission might leave their position to chase after enemy "
"aircraft. The IFV of the vanilla game is notorious for this kind of "
"behavior, breaking formation and leaving the area it should defend "
"against air attacks undefended, often easily lured into an ambush itself."
msgstr ""

#: ../bugfixes/type1/guardapproachtarget.rst:14
msgid ""
"This behavior is fixed in :game:`Ares` and units on Guard mission will no"
" longer leave their position to pursue aircraft when the aircraft goes "
"out of range. Mind that this fix only applies to Guard missions, not Area"
" Guard missions."
msgstr ""

